                  , did steal two wine labels, value 7 s., and a ladle, value 3 s.
            </rs>, his property; and 
               
                  <persName id="t18230409-98-defend917" type="defendantName">
                     JOSEPH 
                     PARTERIDGE
                  <interp inst="t18230409-98-defend917" type="surname" value="PARTERIDGE"></interp>
